text: Otto Kestola (born 20 May 1936) is a Finnish gymnast. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Finland Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Vyborg
